			   <title class="- topic/title ">
				     <ph outputclass="topicnum" class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5349.501-70</ph> Special Termination Costs</title>
			   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
				     <ol class="- topic/ol ">
					       <li outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/li ">
						         <p outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/p ">INTERIM CHANGE:  See <xref href="https://cs2.eis.af.mil/sites/10059/afcc/knowledge_center/Documents/Contracting_Memos/Policy/19-C-11.pdf"
                        scope="external"
                        format="pdf"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">CPM 19-C-11</u>
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">.</u>
							           </xref>
						         </p>
					       </li>
					       <li outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/li ">
						         <p outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/p ">(a) The contracting officer must process requests to use DFARS <ph outputclass="DFARS" class="- topic/ph ">252.249-7000</ph>, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Special Termination Costs</i>, through the SCO to <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-aq.mbx.saf-aqc-workflow@mail.mil"
                        scope="external"
                        format="mailto"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/AQC</u>
							           </xref> (see <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" format="dita" href="MP5349.dita">MP5349</xref><ph class="- topic/ph ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">).</u>
							           </ph>
						         </p>
					       </li>
					       <li id="li__Toc351654717" outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/li ">
						         <p outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/p ">(c)  The contracting officer must forward a request for SAF/FM approval through their SCO and <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-aq.mbx.saf-aqc-workflow@mail.mil"
                        scope="external"
                        format="mailto"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/AQC</u>
							           </xref>
							           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> </b>prior to authorizing any increase in the Government's maximum liability under the clause.  <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-aq.mbx.saf-aqc-workflow@mail.mil"
                        scope="external"
                        format="mailto"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/AQC</u>
							           </xref> will forward the request to <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-fm.mbx.saf-fmp-workflow@mail.mil"
                        scope="external"
                        format="mailto"
                        class="- topic/xref ">
								             <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/FM</u>
							           </xref>.</p>
